THIRD-PARTY ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS

This project implements Proton's SRP-6a authentication protocol based on the
publicly documented behaviour of the ProtonMail go-srp library and the
proton-python-client constants.py file. No source code from those projects is
copied directly; this is an independent Rust implementation. References are
provided in the source comments.

The embedded Proton SRP modulus verification public key was obtained from
https://github.com/ProtonMail/proton-python-client (constants.py). Its
fingerprint is documented in the source code.
